title: Added Google Play licensing support - tested, works, but not used.  It slows…
message:
Added Google Play licensing support - tested, works, but not used.  It slows launch, and serves not purpose for a free app without in-app billing.

Added framework for in-app billing for accepting donations.  Not implemented.

Added share feature - tested, works.

Added code to respond to menu/action bar actions, currently does nothing.

Streamlined miscellaneous code.

Icons are now prettier throughout.

About dialog now works.

Now officially licensed under the MIT license.

First run dialog briefly explains the app
